flowchart TD
    A[Start Device Health Check] --> B[Load Health Check Configuration]
    B --> C[Initialize Diagnostic Tools]
    C --> D[Check System Requirements]
    
    D --> E{Meets Minimum Requirements?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Begin Comprehensive Checks]
    E -->|No| G[Log System Requirements Failure]
    G --> H[Generate Requirements Report]
    H --> Z[End Health Check: Failed]
    
    F --> I[Check Disk Health]
    I --> J[Check Memory Status]
    J --> K[Verify Network Connectivity]
    K --> L[Check CPU Performance]
    L --> M[Verify OS Integrity]
    
    M --> N[Check BitLocker Status]
    N --> O[Scan for Malware]
    O --> P[Check Battery Health]
    P --> Q[Verify Boot Configuration]
    Q --> R[Check Driver Status]
    
    R --> S[Verify Application State]
    S --> T[Check Windows Update Status]
    T --> U[Verify User Profile Integrity]
    
    U --> V[Compile Health Results]
    V --> W{All Checks Passed?}
    
    W -->|Yes| X[Generate Success Report]
    W -->|No| Y[Identify Failed Components]
    Y --> AA[Categorize Issues]
    
    AA --> AB{Severity Level}
    AB -->|Critical| AC[Flag as Migration Blocker]
    AB -->|Warning| AD[Add to Migration Warnings]
    AB -->|Info| AE[Add to Migration Notes]
    
    AC --> AF[Generate Remediation Steps]
    AD --> AF
    AE --> AF
    
    AF --> AG[Compile Health Report]
    X --> AG
    
    AG --> AH[Store Results in Log]
    AH --> AI[Return Health Status]
    AI --> AJ[End Health Check: Complete] 